 particles. Together with fluorescence\nmeasurement from fND, we observed a correlation between the fluorescent signal\nand the size of fND. Our results showed that the axial pattern of iSCAT\ncontrast provides sufficient information for the size of spherical particles.\nOur method enables us to measure the size of nanoparticles from tens of\nnanometers and beyond the Rayleigh limit with nanometer precision, making a\nversatile all-optical nanometric technique.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2022 01:56:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
