 clustering parameter $\\sigma_8$ are shifted\nfrom their $\\Lambda$CDM-like values. This fact makes future surveys, especially\nthose focused on weak lensing measurements, unique tools to test the nature and\nthe couplings of the dark energy sector.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2022 14:28:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-30"}
